				\begin{document}$$\hat{t}$$\end{document}, while the untagged jet is written as j^\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\hat{j}$$\end{document}.

The reconstruction of the pseudo top quark starts from its decay products: the W boson and the b-tagged jet. The W boson is reconstructed from the charged lepton and the neutrino at particle level. The z component of the neutrino momentum, pz(ν)\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
