				\begin{document}$$p_y$$\end{document} such that the imaginary part vanishes and at the same time the transverse components of the neutrino momentum are kept as close as possible to the ETmiss\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
