				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$|y(\hat{t})|$$\end{document}, of the pseudo top quark and pseudo top antiquark. In addition, they are measured as a function of the transverse momentum, pT(j^)\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
